which determines the directions in a sheet material in respect to the rolling direction. Rolled sheet direction is a part of material or object.</rdfs:comment>
        <rdfs:label xml:lang="en">rolled sheet direction</rdfs:label>
        <skos:definition xml:lang="en">Rolled sheet direction is a fiat line which is part of rolled material&apos;s intrinsic reference frame.</skos:definition>
    </owl:Class>
    


