        <rdfs:label xml:lang="en">peak magnetic polarization in the transversal direction</rdfs:label>
        <skos:definition xml:lang="en">Peak magnetic polarization in the transversal direction is a peak magnetic polarization measured exclusively in the transversal direction of an electrical sheet.</skos:definition>
